OL,3,CMajor fire leaves three properties
OL,4,Cdamaged
OL,6,FDozens of firefighters have spent the
OL,7,Fnight tackling a fire which tore
OL,8,Fthrough the roofs of three properties
OL,9,Fon the Isle of Wight.
OL,11,FCrews from Hampshire and Isle of Wight
OL,12,FFire and Rescue Service were called to
OL,13,Fthe scene at Ronsons Close, in Cowes,
OL,14,Fshortly before 3.30am this morning.
OL,16,FAround 30 firefighters attended,
OL,17,Falongside an aerial ladder platform.
OL,19,FThe fire is now under control, with
OL,20,Fcrews maintaining a presence to dampen
OL,21,Fdown the scene.
